FILE: .claude/skills/prisma/SKILL.md
---
---
name: prisma
description: Prisma ORM patterns ‚Äî schema design, migrations, typed queries, and connection pooling.
---

# Prisma Conventions

## Client Singleton
```typescript
import { PrismaClient } from '@prisma/client';
const g = globalThis as { prisma?: PrismaClient };
export const prisma = g.prisma ?? new PrismaClient({ log: ['error'] });
if (process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production') g.prisma = prisma;
```

## Schema
```prisma
model User {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  email     String   @unique
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt
}
```

## Migrations
```bash
npx prisma migrate dev --name describe_change
npx prisma migrate deploy   # production
```

